{"tid":1659801,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"雅居樂建「肇慶香港城」　警員佐級協會：爭取最優惠價格團購","createTime":"2019-10-17T06:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T11:44:30.000Z","uid":289745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07b4125651f55bccc89457fb72e459b7bdf682ca","tid":1659801,"uid":289745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:56:35.000Z","msg":"好行唔送<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察員佐級協會主席林志偉昨日向會員發信，指協會聯同政府華員會，向雅居樂集團商討，在鄰近肇慶東站建立「肇慶香港城」，為退休警員及公務員，提供「生活養老選擇」，構思已進入實踐階段，預計第一期於明年底落成。<br />\n<br />\n信中又指，協會聯同政府華員會會盡量與雅居樂爭取「最優惠價格」團購。<br />\n<br />\n信中指，有見於公務員遇上退休住屋問題，加上在「粵港澳大灣區特別合作試驗區」（簡稱：大灣區）帶動下，希望在肇慶建立具有「港式生活」的特色社區，務求「以低成本，享高質素生活」，包括各種生活所需以至安老養老。"},{"pid":"e7807a7accfcdea8650966a3ac02cadf48f02e01","tid":1659801,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:56:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bf175fefe2e5854ee23752487873a581710ee60e","tid":1659801,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:00:57.000Z","msg":"再收回佣 fatfat啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975f24da3463b0ff6106340eab49c7365389f446","tid":1659801,"uid":327746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:03:15.000Z","msg":"去啦去啦, 唔好等退休, 起好就馬上返去擁抱大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7a5268e04c34d883d37275299e3f6f0a43b83f","tid":1659801,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:04:19.000Z","msg":"一班以退休警員為首的港人業主向鎮政府申訴求助，反被官員駡口臭,伸手扣咽喉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640681/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640681/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ff63b16c8d3ea1a332c961bb8d0a8e8